description:
All 59 Mystery Science Theater 3000 shorts Seasons 1 - 10

The following video files were extracted from the MST3K_SHORTS DVD using SmartRipper and encoded to DivX using codec version 6.8.  They are all Video CD quality.

My thanks go out to the person who made the original DVD these came from.  There are higher quality rips out there, but these are a size that make them convenient to reproduce en masse. (The .torrent for this DVD is included.)

I hope Best Brains is not too offended by this, I love Joel &amp; Mike &amp; Kevin &amp; Trace &amp; Mary &amp; Bill &amp; Frank &amp; Josh &amp; all the others who created and kept MST3K alive for so many years!  I do not think making these available will hurt them at all; on the contrary, I hope more people become aware of MST3K and find out about Rifftrax and the other projects they are working on.

Keep circulating the tapes!     

-- FluxCapacitor

